---
title: Bavette Steak in a Demi Glace Sauce with Caramelized Onion Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Green Beans
description: Our bavette steak has such a deep, rich, and gloriously meaty flavor that it could be a stand-alone dish with little more than salt and pepper for seasoning. But we’re still adding some top-notch sides and a full-bodied sauce to this recipe so that it soars above and beyond. Ultra-creamy mashed potatoes with caramelized onion and tender roasted green beans make it filling and hearty, while a demi glace pan sauce that’s spooned on top has savory complexity.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bavette-steak-in-a-demi-glace-sauce-7d839e71.jpg
